data.title: De Haan Logistyk Sp. z o.o. Company Profile - Poland
data.text: De Haan Logistyk Sp. z o.o. is based in Poland, with the head office in Pniewy. The enterprise currently operates in the General Freight Trucking sector. The enterprise was incorporated on January 17, 2003. There are currently Above 250 (2014) people employed by De Haan Logistyk Sp. z o.o..
